casebody.data:
Wednesday, February 14, 1996

MERIT DOCKET

95-2198. State ex rel. Palich v. James.

In Mandamus. On motion for order to show cause. Sua sponte, motion denied and cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Wright and Cook, JJ., dissent and would order briefing on fees.
